<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="de"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="cid:css-76c2d6b5-10d1-4c38-b144-440312222e34@mhtml.blink" />
    
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Video Frame Extractor</title>
    
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
    <h1>► FRAME EXTRACTOR</h1>
    <p>Batch · Intervalle · ZIP — 100% lokal · alle Browser</p>
</div>

<div class="container">

    <div class="info-banner">
        <span class="ib-icon">ℹ️</span>
        <div class="ib-text">
            <strong>Trimm-Skripte werden automatisch mit in die ZIP gepackt.</strong><br>
            1) <strong>Android:</strong> Termux (aus F-Droid installieren) → <code>pkg install ffmpeg</code> → Skript aus ZIP ausführen.<br>
            2) <strong>Windows/Mac:</strong> trim-Skript aus der ZIP in den Clip-Ordner legen und ausführen.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="upload-area" id="uploadArea">
        <span class="icon">📁</span>
        <div class="title">Videos hierher ziehen oder klicken</div>
        <div class="hint">Bis zu 10 Videos gleichzeitig · MP4, MOV, WebM, AVI, MKV</div>
    </div>
    <input type="file" id="fileInput" accept="video/*" multiple="">

    <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-label">Frame-Intervall</div>
        <div class="interval-row">
            <div class="ibt active" data-v="5">Jedes 5.</div>
            <div class="ibt" data-v="10">Jedes 10.</div>
            <div class="ibt" data-v="15">Jedes 15.</div>
            <div class="ibt" data-v="20">Jedes 20.</div>
            <div class="ibt" data-v="25">Jedes 25.</div>
            <div class="ibt" data-v="last">Nur Letztes</div>
        </div>
        <div class="toggle-row">
            <div class="toggle-label">
                Original-Clip mit in ZIP packen
                <span class="toggle-sub">Dateiname: clip_HHMMSS.mp4 · Endframe: clip_HHMMSS.png</span>
            </div>
            <label class="switch">
                <input type="checkbox" id="includeClipToggle">
                <span class="slider"></span>
            </label>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="file-list" id="fileList">
        <div class="fl-header">
            <span>Warteschlange</span>
            <span class="badge" id="fileCount">0 Videos</span>
        </div>
        <div id="fileItems"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="action-row">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" id="startBtn" disabled="">⚡ Verarbeitung starten</button>
        <button class="btn btn-ghost" id="resetBtn">✕ Zurücksetzen</button>
    </div>

    <div class="progress-panel" id="progressPanel">
        <div class="prog-top">
            <span id="progLabel">Verarbeite...</span>
            <span id="progPct">0%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="prog-bar"><div class="prog-fill" id="progFill"></div></div>
        <div class="prog-detail" id="progDetail"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="summary" id="summary">
        <div class="s-icon">✅</div>
        <h2>Fertig!</h2>
        <p id="summaryText"></p>
        <button class="btn btn-dl" id="dlBtn" style="max-width:280px;margin:0 auto;">📦 ZIP herunterladen</button>
    </div>

</div>

<canvas id="canvas"></canvas>




</body></html>
